Har ila yau, ainihin bangaren &gt;&gt; lambobin / sunayen kamfani da dai sauransu ga relays zai taimaka! &gt;&gt; Ko kana ya sauya sheka babban matakin sakonni ko low matakin sakonni kamar pre-amp&gt; daga matakin sakonni?
