Yadda ake da relays haɗa ta da abin da ake tuki? &gt;&gt; Bukata mafi ƙayyadaddu amsa tambayar !! :-)
A matsayin general mulki, ba gudun ba da sanda za su cleanly canjawa audio idan ka yi kokarin tranfer da kewaye tare da lambobin sadarwa.
A amo da ka ji ta tabbata ga na yanzu-yanzu bude da kuma rufe na hanyar.
A noiseless hanyar transfering audio shi ne ya ƙasa da kewaye.
A babban impedance audio haihuwarka a resistive &quot;T&quot; aka gina kusa da halayyar impedance na kewaye.
Grounding da imputs (haɗa ta T) Canza wurin da audio.
A low impedance haihuwarka gidajen wuta yawanci amfani, da kuma bayanai da ake shorted fita ko grounded.
Secondaries ake paralleled a halayyar impedance.
Wani lokaci idan shi wajibi ne don a zahiri canjawa audio, na biyu lamba da ake amfani da kadan takaice da kewaye fitarwa na duration na sharuddan sauyawa lokaci.
Tarho relays ne m, saboda lambobin sadarwa za a iya gyara su &quot;Ka kafin hutu da kuma Vica versa&quot; amma Ban ga wani daga cikin wadannan shekaru.
Nowadys sharuddan sauyawa ne yake aikata electronically da OP amps, da dai sauransu
A labari kewaye da na yi amfani da gina wani m &quot;na gani isolator&quot; ..
Ya kunshi wani resistive photocell da fitila, duk kunsasshen a cikin wani bututu.
Lokacin da fitila ne kashe cell ne babban juriya.
Kunna fitila a da juriya lowers wucewa da audio.
Har yanzu wannan na&#39;urar a cikin wani &quot;T&quot; sauya cikin audio.
Sãɓãwar launukansa fitilar juriya bayar da m girma iko.
Yi amfani 2 m resisters da kana da mahautsini!
